title: Alfie
description:
A webcomic that attempts mixing plot and porn. It's a story about a remote halfling village coming in contact with humans for the first time. Plot jumps between Alfie and Vera. Halfling mother and daughter as they get to know a couple of humans and elves who help them... expand their horizons.
